 }

 class Note {

 }

 class Tag {

 }

 abstract class BaseNode {

 orderIndex: int
 }

 class ParagraphNode {
 text: String
 }

 class ImageNode {
 image: Image
 caption: String
 }

 enum ListType {
 BULLETED
 NUMBERED
 }
 
 interface NodeParent {
 }
